data.plugin-2.yaml:
sonobuoy-config:
  driver: Job
  plugin-name: create-kubernetes-configuration
  result-format: junit
spec:
  env:
  - name: CLIENT_ID
    value: d2508c14-ddcd-41ed-a8e4-1492f37a6daa
  - name: CLIENT_SECRET
    value: 014986b3-50d6-44dd-b231-c1e8d4a808ed
  - name: CLUSTER_NAME
    value: sonobuoy-test
  - name: CLUSTER_RP
    value: Microsoft.Kubernetes

    value: connectedClusters

    value: azure-voting-app

    value: azure-voting-app

  - name: OPERATOR_PARAMS
    value: --git-readonly --git-path=releases/prod
  - name: OPERATOR_SCOPE
    value: namespace
  - name: REPOSITORY_URL
    value: https://github.com/Azure/arc-helm-demo.git
  - name: RESOURCE_GROUP
    value: akkeshar
  - name: SUBSCRIPTION_ID
    value: 1bfbb5d0-917e-4346-9026-1d3b344417f5

    value: 72f988bf-86f1-41af-91ab-2d7cd011db47
